: "We suppose the Liquor Store happens to beclosed, and Mr. Twidower, who is a friend of mine too, turns on his heel togo back to the Library. In the reality of life he perfoms this actionwithout a hitch or hiatus, as simply and unconsciously as we all do, even ifthe artist's critical eye does see--A toi, Vadim."

